cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

The title of the paper suggests that it is related to natural language processing and deep learning. The mention of "unfolding the structure of a document" further supports this. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper could be related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DL (Deep Learning). The mention of "structure" could also indicate that the paper is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
